description:
Jonestown.-.Todeswahn.einer.Sekte.2008.German.Doku.XviD-MYR

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Der Dokumentarfilm enthuellt die wahre und tragische Geschichte des raetselhaften
Priesters und Gruenders des People Temples Jim Jones.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Featuring never-before-seen footage, this documentary delivers a startling new  
look at the Peoples Temple, headed by preacher Jim Jones who, in 1978, led more
than 900 members to Guyana, where he orchestrated a mass suicide via tainted
punch.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
